    <title>配置Spacemacs</title>
    <link href="shijie-xu.github.io/2017/03/24/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AESpacemacs/"/>
    <id>shijie-xu.github.io/2017/03/24/配置Spacemacs/</id>
    <published>2017-03-23T16:05:29.000Z</published>
    <updated>2017-09-14T16:08:47.006Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul><li>安装 Spacemacs，去<a href="https://github.com/syl20bnr/spacemacs" target="_blank" rel="external">官网</a> git clone。</li></ul><ul><li>安装 source code pro 字体，<a href="https://github.com/adobe-fonts/source-code-pro" target="_blank" rel="external">链接</a>。</li><li>安装<a href="http://www.adobe.com/devnet/opentype/afdko.html" target="_blank" rel="external">FDK工具包</a>，在目录下执行<code>./build.sh</code></li></ul><p>，拷贝target目录下的 otf 和 ttf 字体到目录 /usr/local/share/fonts，然后执行 sudo fc-cache （Linux）；或者直接双击安装（Windows）。</p><ul><li>执行emacs –insecure，至此常规安装结束，接下来修复bug，注意spacemacs不使用.emacs文件，最好移除该文件</li><li>emacs的启动太慢，这个锅emacs不背，是helm包惹的祸，将如下代码添加进~/.spacemacs，详见注释中的issuse链接</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">;; https://github.com/syl20bnr/spacemacs/issues/2705</div><div class="line">;; Fix up the startup-time</div><div class="line">(setq tramp-ssh-controlmaster-options &quot;-o ControlMaster=auto -o ControlPath=&apos;tramp.%%C&apos; -o ControlPersist=no&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>针对melpa源网速差的情况，可以使用这个</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">(require &apos;package)  </div><div class="line">(add-to-list &apos;package-archives &apos;(&quot;melpa&quot; . &quot;https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/elpa/melpa/&quot;) t)</div><div class="line">(package-initialize)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>ProofGeneral 照常安装，添加</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">;; Open .v files with Proof General&apos;s Coq mode</div><div class="line">(load &quot;~/.emacs.d/lisp/PG/generic/proof-site&quot;)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>安装company-coq自动补全后需要注意，spacemacs会自动删除orphan packages所以就悲剧了，下次启动时你会发现刚装了包又被删除了，需要添加如下代码进入.spacemacs</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">(defun dotspacemacs/layers ()</div><div class="line">    (setq-default</div><div class="line">   dotspacemacs-additional-packages &apos;(company-coq)</div><div class="line">   ))</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>并在ProofGeneral代码后添加</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div><div class="line">21</div><div class="line">22</div><div class="line">23</div><div class="line">24</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">;; Load company-coq when opening Coq files</div><div class="line">(add-hook &apos;coq-mode-hook #&apos;company-coq-mode)</div><div class="line">(add-hook &apos;coq-mode-hook</div><div class="line">          (lambda ()</div><div class="line">            ( setq-local prettify-symbols-alist</div><div class="line">                         &apos;((&quot;Alpha&quot; . ?Α) (&quot;Beta&quot; . ?Β) (&quot;Gamma&quot; . ?Γ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Delta&quot; . ?Δ) (&quot;Epsilon&quot; . ?Ε) (&quot;Zeta&quot; . ?Ζ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Eta&quot; . ?Η) (&quot;Theta&quot; . ?Θ) (&quot;Iota&quot; . ?Ι)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Kappa&quot; . ?Κ) (&quot;Lambda&quot; . ?Λ) (&quot;Mu&quot; . ?Μ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Nu&quot; . ?Ν) (&quot;Xi&quot; . ?Ξ) (&quot;Omicron&quot; . ?Ο)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Pi&quot; . ?Π) (&quot;Rho&quot; . ?Ρ) (&quot;Sigma&quot; . ?Σ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Tau&quot; . ?Τ) (&quot;Upsilon&quot; . ?Υ) (&quot;Phi&quot; . ?Φ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Chi&quot; . ?Χ) (&quot;Psi&quot; . ?Ψ) (&quot;Omega&quot; . ?Ω)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;alpha&quot; . ?α) (&quot;beta&quot; . ?β) (&quot;gamma&quot; . ?γ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;delta&quot; . ?δ) (&quot;epsilon&quot; . ?ε) (&quot;zeta&quot; . ?ζ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;eta&quot; . ?η) (&quot;theta&quot; . ?θ) (&quot;iota&quot; . ?ι)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;kappa&quot; . ?κ) (&quot;lambda&quot; . ?λ) (&quot;mu&quot; . ?μ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;nu&quot; . ?ν) (&quot;xi&quot; . ?ξ) (&quot;omicron&quot; . ?ο)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;pi&quot; . ?π) (&quot;rho&quot; . ?ρ) (&quot;sigma&quot; . ?σ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;tau&quot; . ?τ) (&quot;upsilon&quot; . ?υ) (&quot;phi&quot; . ?φ)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;chi&quot; . ?χ) (&quot;psi&quot; . ?ψ) (&quot;omega&quot; . ?ω)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;\\\\&quot; . ?⇓)(&quot;|-&gt;&quot; . ?↦)(&quot;:=&quot; . ?≜)(&quot;\\in&quot; .?∈)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;~&quot; .?¬)(&quot;Proof.&quot; . ?∵) (&quot;Qed.&quot; . ?■)</div><div class="line">                           (&quot;Defined.&quot; . ?□) (&quot;Time&quot; . ?⏱) (&quot;Admitted.&quot; . ?😱)))))</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以上是一些字符的显示</p><ul><li>最后可以添加如下代码在.spacemacs文件头部</li></ul><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">;;Show lineno</div><div class="line">(global-linum-mode t)</div><div class="line">;;Hide tool bar</div><div class="line">(tool-bar-mode -1)</div><div class="line">;;Set cursor mode &apos;bar for 束线 &apos;box for 方块</div><div class="line">(setq-default cursor-type &apos;bar)</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;安装 Spacemacs，去&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/syl20bnr/spacemacs&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;external&quot;&gt;官网&lt;/a&gt; git clone。&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
      
    
    </summary>
    
    
